name: Boba Fett, Bounty Hunter (V)
Lore: 'The most feared bounty hunter in the galaxy. Justifiably, his fee is as large as his reputation.',
Text: 'Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots.  May ''fly'' (landspeed = 3).  Adds one battle destiny if with your alien or Imperial. Immune to attrition < 3 (< 5 if with Vader or a bounty hunter).',
